{"sn1.34:0.1":"Samyutta Nikaya 1.34 ","sn1.34:0.2":"4. Satullapakayikavagga ","sn1.34:0.3":"Nasantisutta ","sn1.34:1.1":"Ekam samayam bhagava savatthiyam viharati jetavane anathapindikassa arame. ","sn1.34:1.2":"Atha kho sambahula satullapakayika devatayo abhikkantaya rattiya abhikkantavanna kevalakappam jetavanam obhasetva yena bhagava tenupasankamimsu; upasankamitva bhagavantam abhivadetva ekamantam atthamsu. ","sn1.34:1.3":"Ekamantam thita kho eka devata bhagavato santike imam gatham abhasi: ","sn1.34:2.1":"“Na santi kama manujesu nicca, ","sn1.34:2.2":"Santidha kamaniyani yesu baddho; ","sn1.34:2.3":"Yesu pamatto apunagamanam, ","sn1.34:2.4":"Anaganta puriso maccudheyya”ti. ","sn1.34:3.1":"“Chandajam agham chandajam dukkham, ","sn1.34:3.2":"Chandavinaya aghavinayo; ","sn1.34:3.3":"Aghavinaya dukkhavinayo”ti. ","sn1.34:4.1":"“Na te kama yani citrani loke, ","sn1.34:4.2":"Sankapparago purisassa kamo; ","sn1.34:4.3":"Titthanti citrani tatheva loke, ","sn1.34:4.4":"Athettha dhira vinayanti chandam. ","sn1.34:5.1":"Kodham jahe vippajaheyya manam, ","sn1.34:5.2":"Samyojanam sabbamatikkameyya; ","sn1.34:5.3":"Tam namarupasmimasajjamanam, ","sn1.34:5.4":"Akincanam nanupatanti dukkha. ","sn1.34:6.1":"Pahasi sankham na vimanamajjhaga, ","sn1.34:6.2":"Acchecchi tanham idha namarupe; ","sn1.34:6.3":"Tam chinnagantham anigham nirasam, ","sn1.34:6.4":"Pariyesamana najjhagamum; ","sn1.34:6.5":"Deva manussa idha va huram va, ","sn1.34:6.6":"Saggesu va sabbanivesanesu”ti. ","sn1.34:7.1":"“Tance hi naddakkhum tathavimuttam, ","sn1.34:7.2":"(iccayasma mogharaja) ","sn1.34:7.3":"Deva manussa idha va huram va; ","sn1.34:7.4":"Naruttamam atthacaram naranam, ","sn1.34:7.5":"Ye tam namassanti pasamsiya te”ti. ","sn1.34:8.1":"“Pasamsiya tepi bhavanti bhikkhu, ","sn1.34:8.2":"(mogharajati bhagava) ","sn1.34:8.3":"Ye tam namassanti tathavimuttam; ","sn1.34:8.4":"Annaya dhammam vicikiccham pahaya, ","sn1.34:8.5":"Sangatiga tepi bhavanti bhikkhu”ti. "}